lead_paragraph: The New-Haven Journal of yesterday retracts its statement of Wednesday, in relation to Bowen McNamee, of this city, and explains the matter thus: "A paragraph was published in our paper yesterday morning, stating that the firm of Bowen McNamee, of New-York, had-failed.
